snippet.title: Yume Nikki Fangame playthrough - Daughter ver. 0.01c
snippet.description:
Content warnings can be viewed at 3: 04, although nothing in this video actually shows depictions of parental or child abuse.

Read more about this fangame: https://ynfg.yume.wiki/Daughter
Download: https://edevweiss.itch.io/daughter
Dream Diary Jam 5 page: https://itch.io/jam/dream-diary-jam-5

TMESTAMPS:
0:00 Vibing to the title screen music by Myuu 
1:48 Starting the game, Reading the Instructions ITEM, Feeding the pet bird for the first time, Viewing the Doll Collection
5:22 Getting Kitchen Knife FANTASY, exploring the Dollhouses, Getting Unicorn FANTASY
12:51 Exploring the Theatre (Closed), Getting Ziegfeld Girl FANTASY
17:14 Getting Birdcage and Flower FANTASIES
20:52 Killing NPCs until I have 10 dollars (jumpcut)
24:00 Buying Rose and Cat MENU TYPES for 5 dollars each, trying the Menu Types on
26:00 Exploring the Theatre (Open), Seeing Theatre EVENT
30:07 Edel vibes to the save theme
